Package kodkod.ast.operator

Contains operators for Kodkod formulas, expressions, and integer expressions.

See:
          Description

Enum Summary
ExprCastOperator Enumerates expression 'cast' operators.
ExprCompOperator Enumerates relational comparison operators.
ExprOperator Enumerates unary (~, ^, *), binary (+, &, ++, ->, -, .) and nary (+, &, ++, ->) expression operators.
FormulaOperator Enumerates binary (&&, ||, =>, <=>) and nary (&&, ||) logical operators.
IntCastOperator Represents an intexpression 'cast' operator.
IntCompOperator Enumerates binary comparison operators: =, < , >, <=, >=.
IntOperator Enumerate unary (-, ~, abs, sgn), binary (+, *, &, |, -, /, %, >>, >>>, <<) and nary (+, *, &, |) operators on integer expressions.
Multiplicity Represents the multiplicity of an expression in a MultiplicityFormula or the multiplicity of a variable in a Decl.
Quantifier Enumerates logical quantifiers.
